snippet.title: MEATBALL the MITE (Jam trailer)
snippet.description:
Here it is. My first metroidvania AND proper jam entry. (except it was late by a few seconds, thankfully they let me submit a pinch late!)
Its not exactly the best interms of level design but I tried my best. I joined late and development only took place over 12 days!

If people like the games idea/vibe enough I might remake it and turn it into a proper, 'fleshed' out game. 

Play here!!! VVVVVVV

https://pinpan.itch.io/meatball-the-mite
